entries.title_d: Set up to intercept for the Ay'Nat pirates advancing on the main target, the RSF Madersim.
entries.title: Corellia System: Destroy the Ay'Nat Pirates
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Get out to the Madersim's last known position.  I fear they will be under attack soon with insufficient protection. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_location_d: An area in the Corellia System where we expect the Ay'Nat pirates to make an appearance
entries.quest_helpallies_d: These were taking from the RSF Madersim, to lose them would be failure on your part
entries.quest_findbattle_d: Travel here to set up the ambush for the Ay'Nat pirates
entries.found_loc: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 We pulled these ships from the Madersim's escort and cannot afford to lose them.  Defend as much as possible \#pcontrast3 >
entries.enemies_win: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 The Madersims' escort has been destroyed, this is unacceptable. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.enemies_remaining: An enemy craft has been destroyed, %DI remain.
entries.enemies_remain: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 An enemy craft has been destroyd, %DI remain. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.enemies_arrived: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Hostile craft are approaching. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.battle_started: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Enemy forces have been engaged. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.assigned_delayed: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Proceed to the following waypoint. We are expecting to intercept a large number of enemy fighters and have diverted some of the Madersims' escort to assist you.  We cannot afford to lose those escorts.  Command out! \#pcontrast3 >
entries.allies_win: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 The mission is a success, enemy fighters have all been destroyed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.allies_remaining: An allied craft has been destroyed, %DI remain.
entries.allies_remain: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 An Allied Craft has been destroyed, %DI remain. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.allies_arrived: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Your backup has arrived.  Good luck. \#pcontrast3 >
